						<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Comprehensive fields for work experience, skills assessment, and professional achievements that recruiters want to see.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl">
						<div class="text-4xl mb-6">üì±</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Modern Web</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Support for social profiles, digital portfolios, and modern web presence including GitHub, LinkedIn, and personal websites.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl">
